Description: Three methods of adaptive importance sampling are implemented in this package: 
        Layered Adaptive Importance Sampling (LAIS),
        Adaptive Population Importance Sampling (APIS)
        and Population Monte Carlo (PMC).
        For more details about the methods, please see the following references.
